'''Victor Silverstone''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (3) 1969, 1973, 1985 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (3)
** 0 (3) 1969, 1973, 1985 

===Runners-up===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (3) 1972, 1982, 2000 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (3)
** 0 (3) 1972, 1982, 2000 

